## Priority: High

Scoped styles only prepend `[data-vm-scope="..."]` to selectors. Vue 3's scoped CSS pseudo-classes are needed for real-world styling.

## Scope

- `:deep(.child)` — target child component elements without scope prefix
- `:global(.class)` — emit rule without scope prefix
- `:slotted(.class)` — target slotted content

